- INSTALL

Inkscape >= 0.47
	The user extensions path moved to "~/.config/inkscape/extensions"

On Linux put the content of the archive in ~./inkscape/extensions/.
On Windows unzip the contents to 'Inkscape\share\extensions\' inside your programs folder.

- COMMENT
Tested on Inkscape 0.46
Contact me at brathering82@gmail.com

- Known bugs
	ui float precision is limited to 1
	suffix doesn't support several special chars

